| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3233 — Recovery Inhibition (ragnarlocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9678ea89-4e07-5ecd-9909-faa8ebfa05f9"
